<h2>Web Component Usage</h2>
<p>Bolt Unordered List is a web component, you can simply use <code class="language-html">&lt;bolt-ul&gt;</code> in the markup to make it render. Its inner content is comprised of <code class="language-html">&lt;bolt-li&gt;</code>.</p>
<h3>Example</h3>
<pre class="c-bolt-code-snippet-syntax--light"><code class="language-html">&lt;bolt-ul&gt;
  &lt;bolt-li&gt;Item 1&lt;/bolt-li&gt;
  &lt;bolt-li&gt;Item 2&lt;/bolt-li&gt;
  &lt;bolt-li&gt;Item 3&lt;/bolt-li&gt;
  &lt;bolt-li&gt;Item 4&lt;/bolt-li&gt;
  &lt;bolt-li&gt;Item 5&lt;/bolt-li&gt;
&lt;/bolt-ul&gt;</code></pre>

